Description: This is a Gibson Memphis ES-335 from 2008 in Vintage Sunburst finish and nickel hardware. With its arched top, F-holes and solid maple center block, the semi-hollowbody Electric Spanish 335 has all the raw power of a solidbody, but with the refined elegance of a traditional Gibson archtop. Sporting Classic '57 pickups with true 'Patent Applied For' flavor, this Memphis ES-335 is the perfect guitar for practically any musical setting from jazz and fusion to blues, rock and beyond. This guitar is very lightly used in near mint condition. The guitar has some minor checking (in normal locations) and a few very minor blemishes that I have attempted to show in close up pics... but as you can see, in the larger pictures, the minor checking etc can't been seen. Also, the neck and action are very good. This is sure to become your go-to guitar for almost any gig, recording session or songwriting alone time that you could hope to enjoy. Comes with Gibson case.
